# The committed examples use an in-code demo HMAC secret for deterministic output.
# It is public test material and must never be used operationally.
#
# Production integrations should inject one of:
# AGENT_COMMERCE_DECISION_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PEM="..."
# AGENT_COMMERCE_DECISION_SIGNING_SECRET="..."
# AGENT_COMMERCE_DECISION_AUTHENTICATOR_KEY_ID="..."
# AGENT_COMMERCE_DECISION_VERIFICATION_KEY_REF="..."
